      <description><![CDATA[
        <h2>What's New in 1.7.4</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Fixed Preferences opening as a collapsed sheet on the activation screen — now opens a full resizable Settings window</li>
          <li>License activation shows immediate feedback (spinner, success, or error) instead of failing silently</li>
          <li>Keyforge API errors are surfaced to the user; license keys are trimmed before activation</li>
